Music

I produce ambient, downbeat electronic music. My influences include Radiohead, Burial, Aphex Twin, Booka Shade, James Holden, Luke Abbott, Moderat, The Beatles, The Knife, Deadmau5, Chopin, and good ol' Bach.

Tracks from Soundcloud

Collaborate?

I'm open to collaborating on tracks / producing for vocalists who'd like an electronic arrangement. Get in touch if you're in the Berlin area.

Jack Kinsella calls himself an analyst because it's suitably nondescript and affords him the possibility of being inconsistent in interests. He owns Oxbridge Notes, co-founded Bolivian Express, and co-organises the elite private marketing group, Growth Hacker Berlin. Follow me if you enjoyed my writing.
